item.title: 794 deob
item.dc:creator: @Dragonium Dragonium
item.description:
@Dragonium wrote:

A job well done OP.

I wish I could rep you, but it sadly got removed. But how can I use a client so up-to-date as runescape if the client is without a server? I don’t even know if anyone coded a 790+ client yet. Some people say that if takes merely basic java skills to add EoC into a server. I’m not a coder myself, but I can only change around codes (it’s not too impressive of what I can do, but meh).

OT: I actually don’t know if any EoC’s are going to be released on Moparscape for an extremely long time. The latest revision is 753. We have a long way to go, and we probably won’t catch up to real Runescape anytime soon. Not everyone likes EoC, but I think it’s decent.
